reviewText:
+

Great graphics;
Open World sandbox game;
Nice story;
Nice voice acting, now including the protagonist with VO;
Sound options;
Now it has ingame map;
Various radio stations to choose from and they are great;
Nice resolution options even for laptops;
Purchasable properties;
Drivable vehicles like cars, bikes, heli, boats, etc;
The saturation is great on this one and the game feels more lively.

-

No graphical options apart from resolution option and minor;
Can't swimm, he dies instead;

Played it at 1366 x 768 x 32 with 30 Fps cap, max allowed on my laptop.

Score: 9/10.
